blog.name: zaronart

blog.description:
Zaron's art blog! Generally SFW. Prone to pastel pony nonsense and catgirls.
I am one half of the duo behind Lonely Hooves, the artist behind Shadows Over Trelldain, and the mastermind of a couple other things that may or may not ever see the light of day.
I reblog a lot of other artists' work and the occasional dose of me openning my gaping maw to saw words about things; if you want to just see what atrocities I commit personally with a pen, hit the "MY ART" link down yonder. You can also find my sinister workings over on DeviantART.
